Mónica Randall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C3%B3nica_Randall 0 Mónica Randall (born 18 November 1942) is a Spanish film actress. Randall has made some 110 appearances in film and TV since 1963. She appeared in numerous Spaghetti western films in the 1960s in films such as One Hundred Thousand Dollars for Ringo and has made regular TV appearances since the 1970s.
